title: 820-00165 waters damage, board start but it stop at 0.45A
message:
Check for USB activity; use onboard USB port.
Test the board alone on the desk; nothing else connected, apart of power cable!

Post voltage for pins  7 & 3 of U1950.
Check for corrosion at J/U6100; clean the connector, if needed.
